Package: TraitGraph
Title: Group Psychology Graph Maker
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Lynden", "Jensen", email = "lynden.jensen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0668-2543"))
Description: Provides a suite of functions to generate publication-quality
    visualizations comparing group members on psychological traits or opinions.
    It allows for flexible customization of aesthetics and supports various
    graph layouts to highlight interpersonal dynamics and trait distributions.
